overpowered minutes before the aircraft was to land near the Afghan
border, officials said.
   Karachi airport authorities said there were no other injuries
among the 143 passengers and 13 crew members aboard the A-300
Airbus. The jet, on a domestic flight from Karachi to Quetar,
